San Patrignano Foundation.&#xd;
San Patrignano Foundation is a non-profit foundation whose sole objective is “social solidarity”. It owns a large part of the real estate and is bound to use it exclusively “to freely offer goods, services and initiatives in favor of people who are marginalized and addicted to drugs”.&#xd;
&#xd;
&#xd;
• San Patrignano Rehabilitation Community Cooperative&#xd;
It’s the heart of San Patrignano. It promotes social, welfare, cultural and training activities and those that support school education without profit-making objectives, in order to rehabilitate all kinds of marginalization and drug addiction.&#xd;
&#xd;
San Patrignano Società Agricola cooperative, active in vocational training for the full recovery and social reintegration of former drug addicts  &#xd;
&#xd;
In addition to these, other bodies include San Patrignano School and Training Association and San Patrignano Sport Amateur Association.&#xd;
&#xd;
- See more at: https://www.sanpatrignano.com/about-us/organizational-structure/
